subSections.title: Hanja
subSections.text:
{{ko-hanja|기러기|안}}

# [[wild goose]], whose [[skein]] flies in [[wedge]] or [[cuneiform]], in contrast with [[鵝]] ([[거위]] 아, ''geowi-a''), the [[w:Domesticated goose|domestic goose]] that would not fly at all.

subSections.title: Compounds
subSections.text: * [[家雁]] ([[가안]], ga-an) domestic goose, ''literally'', house goose.
